	(425,3,'2016-03-21 17:03:36','2016-03-21 14:03:36','<p>Across the world on every March 21, the world comes together to celebrate poetry in all its glory.</p><p>No set rules are laid down for how to mark it. Be it any topic, you can read some poetry. You can perform it. You can write a poem. You can pop along and listen to someone read theirs.</p><p>Because poetry is wonderful. It’s pure emotion and truth. And no matter who you are, there’s a poem out there that will touch you the same way we would love this to appeal to you</p><p>To inspire you to fall back in love with poetry, our peer educator <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100007352083758&amp;fref=ts\">Shawn Davis Kawalya</a> has rounded up a poem about safe sex which you should be interested in reading. Check it out;<br /><br /></p><p> </p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">NO SAFE SEX, NO SEX</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">I ask you to use it</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">And you reply \"No\"</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">I tell you that we won\'t have sex</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">And you reply \"So\"</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Is that how you feel?</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You don\'t want to because of that?</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">I thought you loved me</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">But I guess you were just talkin\' smack</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">I want to be safe</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">And you have a problem with it</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You want to do it bare</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">But I don\'t know who you\'ve been with</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">We go back and forth</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">For a real long time </p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You are listening to your opinion</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">And I am listening to mine</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You say live sex</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">I say safe sex</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You keep saying live sex</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">And now there will be no sex</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Five years later</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You calling me from a clinic</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Telling me everything</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">That you got from some belle</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">I cry for you inside</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Because I feel bad for you</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">If you would\'ve listened 2 me back then</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You would not be where you are now, Boo</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"> </p><p> </p>','Here Is A Brilliant Poem About Safe Sex That Made Us Fall In Love With World Poetry Day','','publish','open','open','','here-is-a-brilliant-poem-about-safe-sex-that-made-us-fall-in-love-with-world-poetry-day','','','2017-07-05 14:46:29','2017-07-05 11:46:29','',0,'http://localhost/rahu/?p=425',0,'post','',0),
