	(468,3,'2017-04-27 11:34:42','2017-04-27 08:34:42','<p>Reach A Hand, Uganda (RAHU) and Communication for Development Foundation Uganda (CDFU) through Government of Uganda, UNFPA 8th Country Programme are seeking to contract a firm to develop a Music Video to popularize our latest audio song through the Musical Project aimed at increasing awareness on teenage pregnancy and under-age marriage.</p><p>The video of the song targeting 12-24 year olds, must aim at amplifying the sexual reproductive health and rights (SRHR) messages in the audio, tell the story, challenges and experiences of young people in SRHR. </p><p>Do you think your firm or studio has got what it takes? Check out the terms of reference below and follow instructions to apply.</p>','Does Your Firm Produce Music Videos? If Yes, We’re Looking For You!','','publish','open','open','','does-your-firm-produce-music-videos-if-yes-were-looking-for-you','','','2017-07-05 12:16:44','2017-07-05 09:16:44','',0,'http://localhost/rahu/?p=468',0,'post','',0),
